headline: J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc. Announces Participation in Upcoming Investor Conferences
summary: LOWELL, Ark., January 28, 2025--J.B. Hunt Transport Services, Inc. (NASDAQ: JBHT) will host 1x1 Investor Meetings at the 3rd Annual Evercore ISI Travel & Transport Conference in New York, New York on Wednesday, February 5, 2025.
